==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: kənjēl'
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /kənˈdʒiːl/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /k@n"dZi:l/
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːl|-iːl]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# (''transitive'') To change from a [[liquid]] to [[solid]] [[state]] perhaps by cold
# (''transitive'') To [[coagulate]], make [[curdle]]d or semi-solid as [[gel]] or [[jelly]]
# (''transitive'') To make [[rigid]] or [[immobile]]
# (''intransitive'') To become congealed, [[solidify]] 

====Etymology====
* Middle English: ''[[congelen]]'' 
* Middle French: ''[[congeler]]''
* Latin: ''[[congelare]]''

